title: La Terraza
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Caribbean, Cuban, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Bar-restaurant with Afro-Caribbean decor. Has a vegetarian menu, but you have to ask for it. A few of the dishes are vegan or could possibly be made vegan. Expect pasta with veggies, vegan soup with coconut milk, greens in coconut sauce, fufu, fried plantains and sweet potatoes, bacan. Located on the second floor and has a terrace.
